        "ja": "このサイトで使われているデータは、OpenStreetMapとプロジェクトのデータを組み合わせています。</a>",
        "en": "We are all collecting information about parks with playground equipment and making maps.<br>The data used is a combination of OpenStreetMap and playground equipment for everyone project.</a>"
    },
